items.sentence: You really want to move back to Australia, don't you?
You're not the only one here from Australia, are you?
I'm surprised that you and Tom don't like each other.
Don't you realize that everything Tom said was a lie?
I think that it's highly unlikely that Tom will swim.
Women age faster than men, but they also outlive men.
Tom wanted to stay with Mary for as long as he could.
Tom and Mary went through the haunted house together.
Tom told everyone that Mary knew how to speak French.
Didn't you know that Tom used to be a French teacher?
